sources.title: Eyes of Texas
sources.description: A ranch owner (Francis Ford) turns his place into a home for boys who have lost their fathers in World War II. His evil female lawyer (Nana Bryant) covets the ranch and works in cahoots with Ford's long-lost nephew and a pack of killer dogs to get it. U.S. Marshal Roy Rogers puts an end to her plans.

sources.title: Eyes Of Texas (1948) ROY ROGERS
sources.description:
Stars: Roy Rogers, Trigger, Lynne Roberts
 Director: William Witney

 Lawyer Hattie Waters is after Thad Cameron's money. She tells him she has found his long lost nephew and has him sign a blank will. Then she has him killed and brings in a phony heir to collect. Marshal Roy Rogers arrives to investigate Thad's death and immediately becomes suspicious. Thad was reportedly killed by wolves but Roy realizes it was really dogs.
